title: The morning after you find out it’s damn hard to be a parent these days.

description: My mom and I dive into differences of being a parent now vs. back when she was, her first impression of Matthew, and how she handled hearing here daughter was diagnosed with a brain tumor. Just talking about real parent shit, no filters.
